Attributes
Name: Introduce Clea3 Optical Imaging System (OIS)
Category: New Product Introduction (NPI)
Description (summary): The Optical Imaging System (OIS) needs to be compatible with FD20 FlexArm configuration (Clea 3).
Proposed Solution (summary): Puma project is introducing the compatibility of Optical Imaging System with FD20 FlexArm configuration (Clea 3).

The following buy items are introduced:
- A new Clea 3 OIS Rotation Unit,
- A new OIS Frontal Stand cable set,

The following make item is introduced:
- A new C-arc Sleeve OIS assy
